28:08.728 --> 28:10.105
- "Mirror, mirror, on the wall,

28:10.188 --> 28:11.981
I am my mother after all."

28:12.065 --> 28:13.775
Oh, that's so lovely, thank you.

28:13.858 --> 28:16.069
{\an3}Mom, were you trying to be,
