28:16.152 --> 28:17.987
'Cause it doesn't sound
like you're, like, okay.

28:18.071 --> 28:20.782
- No, I'm excited because...
- Oh, that's so nice.

28:20.865 --> 28:22.200
{\an1}- It's a furniture store
and I got it

28:22.283 --> 28:23.660
in a pillow for you, yeah.

28:23.743 --> 28:25.453
- Well, I don't know
where this will fit.

28:25.537 --> 28:27.080
{\an1}- Well, you can put it
on your bed.

28:27.163 --> 28:28.915
{\an1}You could put it on the couch.
