28:28.998 --> 28:30.458
{\an3}- Yeah.

28:30.542 --> 28:31.793
{\an1}- So what all are you
gonna have in your store?

28:31.876 --> 28:33.670
- Everything.
- Well, you know what?

28:33.753 --> 28:36.256
{\an1}I'm excited to see
the store space.

28:36.339 --> 28:37.632
{\an3}- Yeah.

28:37.715 --> 28:39.008
{\an1}- Well, whatever way
I can help that--

28:39.092 --> 28:40.427
I would be happy to.
- No, I'll probably just

28:40.510 --> 28:43.221
have you just sit
in there all day.

28:43.304 --> 28:45.557
{\an1}- And I'll just do like
I did over at Froco.

28:45.640 --> 28:48.101
{\an1}I just stood there
and just kept getting it done.

28:48.184 --> 28:49.936
{\an3}- Everyone's just ready
to have it open.

28:50.019 --> 28:51.312
{\an3}So am I.

28:51.396 --> 28:53.440
- And I'm proud of you, Farrah.

28:53.523 --> 28:57.360
<i>♪ ♪</i>

29:01.614 --> 29:04.534
