29:36.941 --> 29:40.320
{\an1}- Cleaned up, pulled some weeds,
bunch of stuff.

29:40.403 --> 29:42.614
- You seem happy.

29:42.697 --> 29:44.199
- Good day's work
makes you happy.

29:44.282 --> 29:45.325
{\an3}- Yeah?

29:45.408 --> 29:46.576
- You feel better?
- Mm-hmm.

29:46.659 --> 29:48.036
- Yeah?
- It helps.

29:48.119 --> 29:49.871
- Keep you occupied...
- Yeah.

29:49.954 --> 29:51.915
- Don't get bored and don't try
to overthink too much.

29:51.998 --> 29:53.041
