your friends,

30:19.317 --> 30:20.735
like, if I was like, oh--

30:20.818 --> 30:22.195
{\an3}- Oh, yeah, we have to approve
of all friends.

30:22.278 --> 30:23.863
- So, who you
going out with tonight?

30:23.947 --> 30:25.198
