30:25.281 --> 30:25.907
- We have a whole
checklist before--

30:25.990 --> 30:27.617
- Can we meet them?
- What?

30:27.700 --> 30:29.369
{\an3}- We have hair length
restrictions.

30:29.452 --> 30:31.454
{\an3}They'll all pee in a cup
when they walk in the house.

30:31.538 --> 30:33.748
Oh, yeah.
- Yeah.

30:33.831 --> 30:36.334
- Kind of gives us
something to do,

30:36.417 --> 30:38.419
'cause I don't want to get
all sad or weird but, like,

30:38.503 --> 30:39.879
I don't have Leah all the time.

30:39.963 --> 30:42.465
I get in the mom stage,
